description:
This episode focuses on reconstructing the baconator. The old one worked fine but I wasn't totally happy with it.

The new baconator allows me to collect cooked pork chops. It properly separates wolves from pigs without injuring either mobs. 

It also separates pig drops from the main item collection point which will work out better for me. Mixing the pig drops with the hostile mob drops had problems with always filling up my inventory with pork when I didn't want it.
